This is the complete source code for Chapter 4 of Real-Time Web Application Development with Vert.x.



To run the application, type:

    vertx run app.js



Then point your web browser to http://localhost:8080

The files included:
* app.js - The deployment verticle
* mindmaps.js - Mind map management verticle
* mindmap_editor.js - Mind map editor verticle
* web/index.html - The application's HTML host page
* web/client.js - The client-side code of the application
* web/editor.js - The client-side code for the mind map editor
* web/mindmap_utils.js - Mindmap utility functions, shared between client and server
* web/style.css - Application stylesheet